<title>USA: Emerson Radio Corp Q3 Dec 31 loss widens.</title>
<headline>Emerson Radio Corp Q3 Dec 31 loss widens.</headline>
<dateline>PARSIPPANY, N.J. 1997-02-19</dateline>
<text>
<p>1996			1995</p>
<p> Shr loss		   $0.14     loss	 $0.11</p>
